		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Have you ever tried using a lot of small blank PCBs to solder in components and then solder flexible wires to other small PCBs, and then you have an ugly baby mobile of PCBs all hanging around everywhere.  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_lol.gif" alt=":lol:" title="Laughing" />

		

